{"tid":1761090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛丁堡集會 部分嘉賓節錄及啟示","createTime":"2019-11-28T16:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T18:28:01.000Z","uid":100155,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"82bca58efdca575a858c5486c73e97e9be1d6ad3","tid":1761090,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"愛丁堡集會<br />\n部分嘉賓節錄<br />\n<br />\nGphone:<br />\n人權法還要感激：海外手足團隊，本地前線手足，同區選有份投票嘅你地（區選show個民意令侵侵簽條Act)<br />\n<br />\n今晚會透過視像形式出席加拿大國會聽證會<br />\n<br />\n唔記得邊個講：<br />\nWhy HK important to CN?<br />\nChina's 74% foreign ipo &amp; bonds to foreign are arranged through HK <br />\nChina's 79% foreign FDI are through HK<br />\n<br />\nSunny: <br />\n未來還有Be Water Act及一系列關於香港嘅法案，我地要大力支持！<br />\n<br />\nAbout HK Act:<br />\n我地已整左300頁嘅制裁名單報告 之後會交比國會及白宮<br />\n<br />\n在HK Act下，侵侵係唔可以唔做嘢<br />\n<br />\n關於制裁：<br />\nSanctions imposed might be subject to 5 yr review. The congress will rediscuss whether sanctions imposed will continue depending on HK's human rights&amp; democracy situation.<br />\n<br />\n關於英國：<br />\n英國議院亦開始有聲出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗候選區議員（我唔記得名）：<br />\nDistrict council is great chance for民間外交 &amp; make HK more connected to other cities. E.g. can help HK be &quot;姐妹城市&quot; with other cities like London.<br />\n<br />\n我地上任後區議會調查721 事件（可能係傳召警隊指揮官）<br />\n亦會與日本大城市的區議員交流,to motivate them do their district sanction on police etc.<br />\n<br />\nSunny encouraged more ppl to do tweeter<br />\n<br />\n區樂軒：日本也很重要 因為如果國會同政府做野，將會係東亞第一塊骨牌 推動其他東亞國家人權法同圍堵中共。<br />\n<br />\nSolomon：贏到立法會就可以推雙普選。It is hard, it is impossible 但我們會幫你們取得勝利！<br />\n<br />\n吳叡人（台灣的研究中國學者）：<br />\nHK Let them recalled 828 &amp; white terror period.<br />\n<br />\n安倍內閣比較想從一帶一路獲利 比較忽略香港但執政黨（自民）同幾個在野黨都有為港發聲<br />\n<br />\n南韓文政府十分親中&amp; not care abt hk.<br />\nBut HK students touched KR students to stand together with HK, 因爲令他們想起1987 六月革命及光洲事件(armies massacred students)<br />\n<br />\nWe need to have the world stand with us. And let the world contain evil communist superstate China.<br />\n<br />\n此刻我們都係香港人，捍衛民主自由人權。<br />\n香港人的抗爭亦令世界憶起自由民主的珍貴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（仲有Ted Cruz, Rick Scott, Hocc, HKDC主席,牧師及其他人講野）"},{"pid":"ccb44480e6e869ce4cbf8252b4d85f7fb2e47434","tid":1761090,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c13762e57b5fb1056dc6b11cf230497108ced04","tid":1761090,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"泡菜果條友快d下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又親中又親朝cls<br />\n左仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfe353c26b651feb138450c055829dce48af00e","tid":1761090,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:18:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58c86d795d99c24a6fdeed8c865fbf64b3b5a73e","tid":1761090,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c13762e57b5fb1056dc6b11cf230497108ced04","tid":1761090,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"泡菜果條友快d下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又親中又親朝cls<br />\n左仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"Connect民間！！民意推動國會及政府！"},{"pid":"557579f2a2a04b178bf5b406dd173f84d80bdb51","tid":1761090,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11d07f0c11ee086d05aceda2a9279fad44d7bbf0","tid":1761090,"uid":100155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"漏左：solomon 之後會去華盛頓DC同朋友商議點樣幫香港人贏立法會"},{"pid":"6fa800bd0b353358803ecb7302a1b5acfb925fc2","tid":1761090,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"721fc7f81dce4ae93cfca467a1834cf226e64002","tid":1761090,"uid":811